87static bool allowsWebsiteDataRecordsForAllOrigins;
88void WebsiteDataStore::allowWebsiteDataRecordsForAllOrigins()
89{
90 allowsWebsiteDataRecordsForAllOrigins = true;
91}
92
93static HashMap<PAL::SessionID, WebsiteDataStore*>& allDataStores()
94{
95 RELEASE_ASSERT(isUIThread());
96 static NeverDestroyed<HashMap<PAL::SessionID, WebsiteDataStore*>> map;
97 return map;
98}
99
100void WebsiteDataStore::forEachWebsiteDataStore(Function<void(WebsiteDataStore&)>&& function)
101{
102 for (auto* dataStore : allDataStores().values())
103 function(*dataStore);
104}
105
106Ref<WebsiteDataStore> WebsiteDataStore::createNonPersistent()
107{
108 return adoptRef(*new WebsiteDataStore(WebsiteDataStoreConfiguration::create(IsPersistent::No), PAL::SessionID::generateEphemeralSessionID()));
109}
110
111Ref<WebsiteDataStore> WebsiteDataStore::create(Ref<WebsiteDataStoreConfiguration>&& configuration, PAL::SessionID sessionID)
112{
113 return adoptRef(*new WebsiteDataStore(WTFMove(configuration), sessionID));
114}
115
116WebsiteDataStore::WebsiteDataStore(Ref<WebsiteDataStoreConfiguration>&& configuration, PAL::SessionID sessionID)
117 : m_sessionID(sessionID)
118 , m_resolvedConfiguration(WTFMove(configuration))
119 , m_configuration(m_resolvedConfiguration->copy())
120 , m_deviceIdHashSaltStorage(DeviceIdHashSaltStorage::create(isPersistent() ? m_configuration->deviceIdHashSaltsStorageDirectory() : String()))
121 , m_queue(WorkQueue::create("com.apple.WebKit.WebsiteDataStore"))
122#if ENABLE(WEB_AUTHN)
123 , m_authenticatorManager(makeUniqueRef<AuthenticatorManager>())
124#endif
125 , m_client(makeUniqueRef<WebsiteDataStoreClient>())
126#if HAVE(APP_SSO)
127 , m_soAuthorizationCoordinator(makeUniqueRef<SOAuthorizationCoordinator>())
128#endif
129{
130 WTF::setProcessPrivileges(allPrivileges());
131 registerWithSessionIDMap();
132 platformInitialize();
133
134 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
135}
136
137WebsiteDataStore::~WebsiteDataStore()
138{
139 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
140 RELEASE_ASSERT(m_sessionID.isValid());
141
142 platformDestroy();
143
144 ASSERT(allDataStores().get(m_sessionID) == this);
145 allDataStores().remove(m_sessionID);
146 networkProcess().removeSession(*this);
147#if ENABLE(GPU_PROCESS)
148 if (auto* gpuProcessProxy = GPUProcessProxy::singletonIfCreated())
149 gpuProcessProxy->removeSession(m_sessionID);
150#endif
151}
152
153static RefPtr<WebsiteDataStore>& globalDefaultDataStore()
154{
155 static NeverDestroyed<RefPtr<WebsiteDataStore>> globalDefaultDataStore;
156 return globalDefaultDataStore.get();
157}
158
159Ref<WebsiteDataStore> WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStore()
160{
161 InitializeWebKit2();
162 auto& store = globalDefaultDataStore();
163 if (!store)
164 store = adoptRef(new WebsiteDataStore(WebsiteDataStoreConfiguration::create(IsPersistent::Yes), PAL::SessionID::defaultSessionID()));
165
166 return *store;
167}
168
169void WebsiteDataStore::deleteDefaultDataStoreForTesting()
170{
171 globalDefaultDataStore() = nullptr;
172}
173
174bool WebsiteDataStore::defaultDataStoreExists()
175{
176 return !!globalDefaultDataStore();
177}
178
179void WebsiteDataStore::registerWithSessionIDMap()
180{
181 auto result = allDataStores().add(m_sessionID, this);
182 ASSERT_UNUSED(result, result.isNewEntry);
183}
184
185WebsiteDataStore* WebsiteDataStore::existingDataStoreForSessionID(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
186{
187 return allDataStores().get(sessionID);
188}
189
190static Ref<NetworkProcessProxy> networkProcessForSession(PAL::SessionID sessionID)
191{
192#if PLATFORM(GTK) || PLATFORM(WPE)
193 if (sessionID.isEphemeral()) {
194 // Reuse a previous persistent session network process for ephemeral sessions.
195 for (auto* dataStore : allDataStores().values()) {
196 if (dataStore->isPersistent())
197 return makeRef(dataStore->networkProcess());
198 }
199 }
200 return NetworkProcessProxy::create();
201#else
202 UNUSED_PARAM(sessionID);
203 return NetworkProcessProxy::ensureDefaultNetworkProcess();
204#endif
205}
206
207NetworkProcessProxy& WebsiteDataStore::networkProcess()
208{
209 if (!m_networkProcess) {
210 m_networkProcess = networkProcessForSession(m_sessionID);
211 m_networkProcess->addSession(*this, NetworkProcessProxy::SendParametersToNetworkProcess::Yes);
212 }
213
214 return *m_networkProcess;
215}
216
217NetworkProcessProxy& WebsiteDataStore::networkProcess() const
218{
219 return const_cast<WebsiteDataStore&>(*this).networkProcess();
220}
221
222void WebsiteDataStore::registerProcess(WebProcessProxy& process)
223{
224 ASSERT(process.pageCount() || process.provisionalPageCount());
225 m_processes.add(process);
226}
227
228void WebsiteDataStore::unregisterProcess(WebProcessProxy& process)
229{
230 ASSERT(!process.pageCount());
231 ASSERT(!process.provisionalPageCount());
232 m_processes.remove(process);
233}
234
235void WebsiteDataStore::resolveDirectoriesIfNecessary()
236{
237 if (m_hasResolvedDirectories)
238 return;
239 m_hasResolvedDirectories = true;
240
241 // Resolve directory paths.
242 if (!m_configuration->applicationCacheDirectory().isEmpty())
243 m_resolvedConfiguration->setApplicationCacheDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->applicationCacheDirectory()));
244 if (!m_configuration->mediaCacheDirectory().isEmpty())
245 m_resolvedConfiguration->setMediaCacheDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->mediaCacheDirectory()));
246 if (!m_configuration->mediaKeysStorageDirectory().isEmpty())
247 m_resolvedConfiguration->setMediaKeysStorageDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->mediaKeysStorageDirectory()));
248 if (!m_configuration->webSQLDatabaseDirectory().isEmpty())
249 m_resolvedConfiguration->setWebSQLDatabaseDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->webSQLDatabaseDirectory()));
250 if (!m_configuration->indexedDBDatabaseDirectory().isEmpty())
251 m_resolvedConfiguration->setIndexedDBDatabaseDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->indexedDBDatabaseDirectory()));
252 if (!m_configuration->alternativeServicesDirectory().isEmpty() && WebsiteDataStore::http3Enabled())
253 m_resolvedConfiguration->setAlternativeServicesDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->alternativeServicesDirectory()));
254 if (!m_configuration->deviceIdHashSaltsStorageDirectory().isEmpty())
255 m_resolvedConfiguration->setDeviceIdHashSaltsStorageDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->deviceIdHashSaltsStorageDirectory()));
256 if (!m_configuration->networkCacheDirectory().isEmpty())
257 m_resolvedConfiguration->setNetworkCacheDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->networkCacheDirectory()));
258 if (!m_configuration->resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory().isEmpty())
259 m_resolvedConfiguration->setResourceLoadStatisticsDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory()));
260 if (!m_configuration->serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory().isEmpty() && m_resolvedConfiguration->serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory().isEmpty())
261 m_resolvedConfiguration->setServiceWorkerRegistrationDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory()));
262 if (!m_configuration->javaScriptConfigurationDirectory().isEmpty())
263 m_resolvedConfiguration->setJavaScriptConfigurationDirectory(resolvePathForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->javaScriptConfigurationDirectory()));
264 if (!m_configuration->cacheStorageDirectory().isEmpty() && m_resolvedConfiguration->cacheStorageDirectory().isEmpty())
265 m_resolvedConfiguration->setCacheStorageDirectory(resolvePathForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->cacheStorageDirectory()));
266 if (!m_configuration->hstsStorageDirectory().isEmpty() && m_resolvedConfiguration->hstsStorageDirectory().isEmpty())
267 m_resolvedConfiguration->setHSTSStorageDirectory(resolvePathForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->hstsStorageDirectory()));
268#if HAVE(ARKIT_INLINE_PREVIEW)
269 if (!m_configuration->modelElementCacheDirectory().isEmpty())
270 m_resolvedConfiguration->setModelElementCacheDirectory(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(m_configuration->modelElementCacheDirectory()));
271#endif
272
273 // Resolve directories for file paths.
274 if (!m_configuration->cookieStorageFile().isEmpty()) {
275 m_resolvedConfiguration->setCookieStorageFile(resolveAndCreateReadWriteDirectoryForSandboxExtension(FileSystem::parentPath(m_configuration->cookieStorageFile())));
276 m_resolvedConfiguration->setCookieStorageFile(FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(m_resolvedConfiguration->cookieStorageFile(), FileSystem::pathFileName(m_configuration->cookieStorageFile())));
277 }
278}
279
280enum class ProcessAccessType {
281 None,
282 OnlyIfLaunched,
283 Launch,
284};
285
286static ProcessAccessType computeNetworkProcessAccessTypeForDataFetch(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, bool isNonPersistentStore)
287{
288 for (auto dataType : dataTypes) {
289 if (WebsiteData::ownerProcess(dataType) == WebsiteDataProcessType::Network) {
290 if (isNonPersistentStore)
291 return ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched;
292 return ProcessAccessType::Launch;
293 }
294 }
295 return ProcessAccessType::None;
296}
297
298static ProcessAccessType computeWebProcessAccessTypeForDataFetch(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, bool isNonPersistentStore)
299{
300 UNUSED_PARAM(isNonPersistentStore);
301
302 ProcessAccessType processAccessType = ProcessAccessType::None;
303
304 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::MemoryCache))
305 return ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched;
306
307 return processAccessType;
308}
309
310void WebsiteDataStore::fetchData(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, Function<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>)>&& completionHandler)
311{
312 fetchDataAndApply(dataTypes, fetchOptions, WorkQueue::main(), WTFMove(completionHandler));
313}
314
315void WebsiteDataStore::fetchDataAndApply(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, Ref<WorkQueue>&& queue, Function<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>)>&& apply)
316{
317 class CallbackAggregator final : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<CallbackAggregator, WTF::DestructionThread::MainRunLoop> {
318 public:
319 static Ref<CallbackAggregator> create(OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, Ref<WorkQueue>&& queue, Function<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>)>&& apply, WebsiteDataStore& dataStore)
320 {
321 return adoptRef(*new CallbackAggregator(fetchOptions, WTFMove(queue), WTFMove(apply), dataStore));
322 }
323
324 ~CallbackAggregator()
325 {
326 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
327
328 Vector<WebsiteDataRecord> records;
329 records.reserveInitialCapacity(m_websiteDataRecords.size());
330 for (auto& record : m_websiteDataRecords.values())
331 records.uncheckedAppend(m_queue.ptr() != &WorkQueue::main() ? crossThreadCopy(record) : WTFMove(record));
332
333 m_queue->dispatch([apply = WTFMove(m_apply), records = WTFMove(records)] () mutable {
334 apply(WTFMove(records));
335 });
336 }
337
338 const OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption>& fetchOptions() const { return m_fetchOptions; }
339
340 void addWebsiteData(WebsiteData&& websiteData)
341 {
342 if (!RunLoop::isMain()) {
343 RunLoop::main().dispatch([protectedThis = makeRef(*this), websiteData = crossThreadCopy(websiteData)]() mutable {
344 protectedThis->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
345 });
346 return;
347 }
348 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
349 for (auto& entry : websiteData.entries) {
350 auto displayName = WebsiteDataRecord::displayNameForOrigin(entry.origin);
351 if (!displayName) {
352 if (!allowsWebsiteDataRecordsForAllOrigins)
353 continue;
354
355 String hostString = entry.origin.host.isEmpty() ? "" : makeString(" ", entry.origin.host);
356 displayName = makeString(entry.origin.protocol, hostString);
357 }
358
359 auto& record = m_websiteDataRecords.add(displayName, WebsiteDataRecord { }).iterator->value;
360 if (!record.displayName)
361 record.displayName = WTFMove(displayName);
362
363 record.add(entry.type, entry.origin);
364
365 if (m_fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes)) {
366 if (!record.size)
367 record.size = WebsiteDataRecord::Size { 0, { } };
368
369 record.size->totalSize += entry.size;
370 record.size->typeSizes.add(static_cast<unsigned>(entry.type), 0).iterator->value += entry.size;
371 }
372 }
373
374 for (auto& hostName : websiteData.hostNamesWithCookies) {
375 auto displayName = WebsiteDataRecord::displayNameForCookieHostName(hostName);
376 if (!displayName)
377 continue;
378
379 auto& record = m_websiteDataRecords.add(displayName, WebsiteDataRecord { }).iterator->value;
380 if (!record.displayName)
381 record.displayName = WTFMove(displayName);
382
383 record.addCookieHostName(hostName);
384 }
385
386#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
387 for (auto& hostName : websiteData.hostNamesWithPluginData) {
388 auto displayName = WebsiteDataRecord::displayNameForHostName(hostName);
389 if (!displayName)
390 continue;
391
392 auto& record = m_websiteDataRecords.add(displayName, WebsiteDataRecord { }).iterator->value;
393 if (!record.displayName)
394 record.displayName = WTFMove(displayName);
395
396 record.addPluginDataHostName(hostName);
397 }
398#endif
399
400 for (auto& hostName : websiteData.hostNamesWithHSTSCache) {
401 auto displayName = WebsiteDataRecord::displayNameForHostName(hostName);
402 if (!displayName)
403 continue;
404
405 auto& record = m_websiteDataRecords.add(displayName, WebsiteDataRecord { }).iterator->value;
406 if (!record.displayName)
407 record.displayName = WTFMove(displayName);
408
409 record.addHSTSCacheHostname(hostName);
410 }
411
412#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
413 for (const auto& domain : websiteData.registrableDomainsWithResourceLoadStatistics) {
414 auto displayName = WebsiteDataRecord::displayNameForHostName(domain.string());
415 if (!displayName)
416 continue;
417
418 auto& record = m_websiteDataRecords.add(displayName, WebsiteDataRecord { }).iterator->value;
419 if (!record.displayName)
420 record.displayName = WTFMove(displayName);
421
422 record.addResourceLoadStatisticsRegistrableDomain(domain);
423 }
424#endif
425 }
426
427private:
428 CallbackAggregator(OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, Ref<WorkQueue>&& queue, Function<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>)>&& apply, WebsiteDataStore& dataStore)
429 : m_fetchOptions(fetchOptions)
430 , m_queue(WTFMove(queue))
431 , m_apply(WTFMove(apply))
432 , m_protectedDataStore(dataStore)
433 {
434 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
435 }
436
437 const OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> m_fetchOptions;
438 Ref<WorkQueue> m_queue;
439 Function<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>)> m_apply;
440
441 HashMap<String, WebsiteDataRecord> m_websiteDataRecords;
442 Ref<WebsiteDataStore> m_protectedDataStore;
443 };
444
445 auto callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create(fetchOptions, WTFMove(queue), WTFMove(apply), *this);
446
447#if ENABLE(VIDEO)
448 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
449 m_queue->dispatch([mediaCacheDirectory = m_configuration->mediaCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
450 WebsiteData websiteData;
451 for (auto& origin : WebCore::HTMLMediaElement::originsInMediaCache(mediaCacheDirectory))
452 websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origin, WebsiteDataType::DiskCache, 0 });
453 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
454 });
455 }
456#endif
457
458 auto networkProcessAccessType = computeNetworkProcessAccessTypeForDataFetch(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
459 switch (networkProcessAccessType) {
460 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
461 networkProcess();
462 ASSERT(m_networkProcess);
463 FALLTHROUGH;
464 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
465 if (m_networkProcess) {
466 m_networkProcess->fetchWebsiteData(m_sessionID, dataTypes, fetchOptions, [callbackAggregator](WebsiteData websiteData) {
467 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
468 });
469 }
470 break;
471 case ProcessAccessType::None:
472 break;
473 }
474
475 auto webProcessAccessType = computeWebProcessAccessTypeForDataFetch(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
476 if (webProcessAccessType != ProcessAccessType::None) {
477 for (auto& process : processes()) {
478 switch (webProcessAccessType) {
479 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
480 if (process.state() != WebProcessProxy::State::Running)
481 continue;
482 break;
483
484 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
485 // FIXME: Handle this.
486 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
487 break;
488
489 case ProcessAccessType::None:
490 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
491 }
492
493 process.fetchWebsiteData(m_sessionID, dataTypes, [callbackAggregator](WebsiteData websiteData) {
494 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
495 });
496 }
497 }
498
499 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DeviceIdHashSalt)) {
500 m_deviceIdHashSaltStorage->getDeviceIdHashSaltOrigins([callbackAggregator](auto&& origins) {
501 WebsiteData websiteData;
502 while (!origins.isEmpty())
503 websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origins.takeAny(), WebsiteDataType::DeviceIdHashSalt, 0 });
504 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
505 });
506 }
507
508 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::OfflineWebApplicationCache) && isPersistent()) {
509 m_queue->dispatch([fetchOptions, applicationCacheDirectory = m_configuration->applicationCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName = m_configuration->applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
510 auto storage = WebCore::ApplicationCacheStorage::create(applicationCacheDirectory, applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName);
511 WebsiteData websiteData;
512 for (auto& origin : storage->originsWithCache()) {
513 uint64_t size = fetchOptions.contains(WebsiteDataFetchOption::ComputeSizes) ? storage->diskUsageForOrigin(origin) : 0;
514 websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origin, WebsiteDataType::OfflineWebApplicationCache, size });
515 }
516 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
517 });
518 }
519
520 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::WebSQLDatabases) && isPersistent()) {
521 m_queue->dispatch([webSQLDatabaseDirectory = m_configuration->webSQLDatabaseDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator]() {
522 WebsiteData websiteData;
523 for (auto& origin : WebCore::DatabaseTracker::trackerWithDatabasePath(webSQLDatabaseDirectory)->origins())
524 websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origin, WebsiteDataType::WebSQLDatabases, 0 });
525 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
526 });
527 }
528
529 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::MediaKeys) && isPersistent()) {
530 m_queue->dispatch([mediaKeysStorageDirectory = m_configuration->mediaKeysStorageDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
531 WebsiteData websiteData;
532 for (auto& origin : mediaKeyOrigins(mediaKeysStorageDirectory))
533 websiteData.entries.append(WebsiteData::Entry { origin, WebsiteDataType::MediaKeys, 0 });
534 callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
535 });
536 }
537
538#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
539 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::PlugInData) && isPersistent()) {
540 class State {
541 public:
542 static void fetchData(Ref<CallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins)
543 {
544 new State(WTFMove(callbackAggregator), WTFMove(plugins));
545 }
546
547 private:
548 State(Ref<CallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins)
549 : m_callbackAggregator(WTFMove(callbackAggregator))
550 , m_plugins(WTFMove(plugins))
551 {
552 fetchWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
553 }
554
555 ~State()
556 {
557 ASSERT(m_plugins.isEmpty());
558 }
559
560 void fetchWebsiteDataForNextPlugin()
561 {
562 if (m_plugins.isEmpty()) {
563 WebsiteData websiteData;
564 websiteData.hostNamesWithPluginData = WTFMove(m_hostNames);
565
566 m_callbackAggregator->addWebsiteData(WTFMove(websiteData));
567
568 delete this;
569 return;
570 }
571
572 auto plugin = m_plugins.takeLast();
573 PluginProcessManager::singleton().fetchWebsiteData(plugin, m_callbackAggregator->fetchOptions(), [this](Vector<String> hostNames) {
574 for (auto& hostName : hostNames)
575 m_hostNames.add(WTFMove(hostName));
576 fetchWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
577 });
578 }
579
580 Ref<CallbackAggregator> m_callbackAggregator;
581 Vector<PluginModuleInfo> m_plugins;
582 HashSet<String> m_hostNames;
583 };
584
585 State::fetchData(callbackAggregator.copyRef(), plugins());
586 }
587#endif
588}
589
590#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
591void WebsiteDataStore::fetchDataForRegistrableDomains(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, OptionSet<WebsiteDataFetchOption> fetchOptions, Vector<WebCore::RegistrableDomain>&& domains, CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>&&, HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain>&&)>&& completionHandler)
592{
593 fetchDataAndApply(dataTypes, fetchOptions, m_queue.copyRef(), [domains = crossThreadCopy(domains), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (auto&& existingDataRecords) mutable {
594 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
595
596 Vector<WebsiteDataRecord> matchingDataRecords;
597 HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> domainsWithMatchingDataRecords;
598 for (auto&& dataRecord : existingDataRecords) {
599 for (auto& domain : domains) {
600 if (dataRecord.matches(domain)) {
601 matchingDataRecords.append(WTFMove(dataRecord));
602 domainsWithMatchingDataRecords.add(domain.isolatedCopy());
603 break;
604 }
605 }
606 }
607 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), matchingDataRecords = WTFMove(matchingDataRecords), domainsWithMatchingDataRecords = WTFMove(domainsWithMatchingDataRecords)] () mutable {
608 completionHandler(WTFMove(matchingDataRecords), WTFMove(domainsWithMatchingDataRecords));
609 });
610 });
611}
612#endif
613
614static ProcessAccessType computeNetworkProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, bool isNonPersistentStore)
615{
616 ProcessAccessType processAccessType = ProcessAccessType::None;
617
618 for (auto dataType : dataTypes) {
619 if (dataType == WebsiteDataType::Cookies) {
620 if (isNonPersistentStore)
621 processAccessType = std::max(processAccessType, ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched);
622 else
623 processAccessType = std::max(processAccessType, ProcessAccessType::Launch);
624 } else if (WebsiteData::ownerProcess(dataType) == WebsiteDataProcessType::Network)
625 return ProcessAccessType::Launch;
626 }
627
628 return processAccessType;
629}
630
631static ProcessAccessType computeWebProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, bool isNonPersistentStore)
632{
633 UNUSED_PARAM(isNonPersistentStore);
634
635 ProcessAccessType processAccessType = ProcessAccessType::None;
636
637 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::MemoryCache))
638 processAccessType = std::max(processAccessType, ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched);
639
640 return processAccessType;
641}
642
643class RemovalCallbackAggregator : public ThreadSafeRefCounted<RemovalCallbackAggregator, WTF::DestructionThread::MainRunLoop> {
644public:
645 static Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator> create(WebsiteDataStore& dataStore, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
646 {
647 return adoptRef(*new RemovalCallbackAggregator(dataStore, WTFMove(completionHandler)));
648 }
649
650 ~RemovalCallbackAggregator()
651 {
652 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
653 RunLoop::main().dispatch(WTFMove(m_completionHandler));
654 }
655
656private:
657 RemovalCallbackAggregator(WebsiteDataStore& dataStore, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
658 : m_protectedDataStore(dataStore)
659 , m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
660 {
661 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
662 }
663
664 Ref<WebsiteDataStore> m_protectedDataStore;
665 CompletionHandler<void()> m_completionHandler;
666};
667
668void WebsiteDataStore::removeData(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, WallTime modifiedSince, Function<void()>&& completionHandler)
669{
670 auto callbackAggregator = RemovalCallbackAggregator::create(*this, WTFMove(completionHandler));
671
672#if ENABLE(VIDEO)
673 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
674 m_queue->dispatch([modifiedSince, mediaCacheDirectory = m_configuration->mediaCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
675 WebCore::HTMLMediaElement::clearMediaCache(mediaCacheDirectory, modifiedSince);
676 });
677 }
678#endif
679
680#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
681 bool didNotifyNetworkProcessToDeleteWebsiteData = false;
682#endif
683 auto networkProcessAccessType = computeNetworkProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
684 switch (networkProcessAccessType) {
685 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
686 networkProcess();
687 ASSERT(m_networkProcess);
688 FALLTHROUGH;
689 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
690 if (m_networkProcess) {
691 m_networkProcess->deleteWebsiteData(m_sessionID, dataTypes, modifiedSince, [callbackAggregator] { });
692#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
693 didNotifyNetworkProcessToDeleteWebsiteData = true;
694#endif
695 }
696 break;
697 case ProcessAccessType::None:
698 break;
699 }
700
701 auto webProcessAccessType = computeWebProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
702 if (webProcessAccessType != ProcessAccessType::None) {
703 for (auto& processPool : processPools()) {
704 // Clear back/forward cache first as processes removed from the back/forward cache will likely
705 // be added to the WebProcess cache.
706 processPool->backForwardCache().removeEntriesForSession(sessionID());
707 processPool->webProcessCache().clearAllProcessesForSession(sessionID());
708 }
709
710 for (auto& process : processes()) {
711 switch (webProcessAccessType) {
712 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
713 if (process.state() != WebProcessProxy::State::Running)
714 continue;
715 break;
716
717 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
718 // FIXME: Handle this.
719 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
720 break;
721
722 case ProcessAccessType::None:
723 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
724 }
725
726 process.deleteWebsiteData(m_sessionID, dataTypes, modifiedSince, [callbackAggregator] { });
727 }
728 }
729
730 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DeviceIdHashSalt) || (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies)))
731 m_deviceIdHashSaltStorage->deleteDeviceIdHashSaltOriginsModifiedSince(modifiedSince, [callbackAggregator] { });
732
733 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::OfflineWebApplicationCache) && isPersistent()) {
734 m_queue->dispatch([applicationCacheDirectory = m_configuration->applicationCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName = m_configuration->applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
735 auto storage = WebCore::ApplicationCacheStorage::create(applicationCacheDirectory, applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName);
736 storage->deleteAllCaches();
737 });
738 }
739
740 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::WebSQLDatabases) && isPersistent()) {
741 m_queue->dispatch([webSQLDatabaseDirectory = m_configuration->webSQLDatabaseDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator, modifiedSince] {
742 WebCore::DatabaseTracker::trackerWithDatabasePath(webSQLDatabaseDirectory)->deleteDatabasesModifiedSince(modifiedSince);
743 });
744 }
745
746 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::MediaKeys) && isPersistent()) {
747 m_queue->dispatch([mediaKeysStorageDirectory = m_configuration->mediaKeysStorageDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator, modifiedSince] {
748 removeMediaKeys(mediaKeysStorageDirectory, modifiedSince);
749 });
750 }
751
752 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::SearchFieldRecentSearches) && isPersistent()) {
753 m_queue->dispatch([modifiedSince, callbackAggregator] {
754 platformRemoveRecentSearches(modifiedSince);
755 });
756 }
757
758#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
759 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::PlugInData) && isPersistent()) {
760 class State {
761 public:
762 static void deleteData(Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins, WallTime modifiedSince)
763 {
764 new State(WTFMove(callbackAggregator), WTFMove(plugins), modifiedSince);
765 }
766
767 private:
768 State(Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins, WallTime modifiedSince)
769 : m_callbackAggregator(WTFMove(callbackAggregator))
770 , m_plugins(WTFMove(plugins))
771 , m_modifiedSince(modifiedSince)
772 {
773 deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
774 }
775
776 ~State()
777 {
778 ASSERT(m_plugins.isEmpty());
779 }
780
781 void deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin()
782 {
783 if (m_plugins.isEmpty()) {
784 delete this;
785 return;
786 }
787
788 auto plugin = m_plugins.takeLast();
789 PluginProcessManager::singleton().deleteWebsiteData(plugin, m_modifiedSince, [this] {
790 deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
791 });
792 }
793
794 Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator> m_callbackAggregator;
795 Vector<PluginModuleInfo> m_plugins;
796 WallTime m_modifiedSince;
797 };
798
799 State::deleteData(callbackAggregator.copyRef(), plugins(), modifiedSince);
800 }
801#endif
802
803#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
804 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::ResourceLoadStatistics)) {
805 if (!didNotifyNetworkProcessToDeleteWebsiteData)
806 networkProcess().deleteWebsiteData(m_sessionID, dataTypes, modifiedSince, [callbackAggregator] { });
807
808 clearResourceLoadStatisticsInWebProcesses([callbackAggregator] { });
809 }
810#endif
811}
812
813void WebsiteDataStore::removeData(OptionSet<WebsiteDataType> dataTypes, const Vector<WebsiteDataRecord>& dataRecords, Function<void()>&& completionHandler)
814{
815 Vector<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
816
817 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
818 for (auto& origin : dataRecord.origins)
819 origins.append(origin);
820 }
821
822 auto callbackAggregator = RemovalCallbackAggregator::create(*this, WTFMove(completionHandler));
823
824 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DiskCache)) {
825 HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
826 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
827 for (const auto& origin : dataRecord.origins)
828 origins.add(crossThreadCopy(origin));
829 }
830
831#if ENABLE(VIDEO)
832 m_queue->dispatch([origins = WTFMove(origins), mediaCacheDirectory = m_configuration->mediaCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
833 WebCore::HTMLMediaElement::clearMediaCacheForOrigins(mediaCacheDirectory, origins);
834 });
835#endif
836 }
837
838 auto networkProcessAccessType = computeNetworkProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
839 if (networkProcessAccessType != ProcessAccessType::None) {
840 auto pools = networkProcessAccessType == ProcessAccessType::Launch ? ensureProcessPools() : processPools();
841 for (auto& processPool : pools) {
842 switch (networkProcessAccessType) {
843 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
844 break;
845
846 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
847 networkProcess();
848 break;
849
850 case ProcessAccessType::None:
851 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
852 }
853
854 Vector<String> cookieHostNames;
855 Vector<String> HSTSCacheHostNames;
856 Vector<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> registrableDomains;
857 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
858 for (auto& hostName : dataRecord.cookieHostNames)
859 cookieHostNames.append(hostName);
860 for (auto& hostName : dataRecord.HSTSCacheHostNames)
861 HSTSCacheHostNames.append(hostName);
862#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
863 for (auto& registrableDomain : dataRecord.resourceLoadStatisticsRegistrableDomains)
864 registrableDomains.append(registrableDomain);
865#endif
866 }
867
868 networkProcess().deleteWebsiteDataForOrigins(m_sessionID, dataTypes, origins, cookieHostNames, HSTSCacheHostNames, registrableDomains, [callbackAggregator, processPool] { });
869 }
870 }
871
872 auto webProcessAccessType = computeWebProcessAccessTypeForDataRemoval(dataTypes, !isPersistent());
873 if (webProcessAccessType != ProcessAccessType::None) {
874 for (auto& process : processes()) {
875 switch (webProcessAccessType) {
876 case ProcessAccessType::OnlyIfLaunched:
877 if (process.state() != WebProcessProxy::State::Running)
878 continue;
879 break;
880
881 case ProcessAccessType::Launch:
882 // FIXME: Handle this.
883 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
884 break;
885
886 case ProcessAccessType::None:
887 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
888 }
889
890 process.deleteWebsiteDataForOrigins(m_sessionID, dataTypes, origins, [callbackAggregator] { });
891 }
892 }
893
894 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::DeviceIdHashSalt) || (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::Cookies))) {
895 m_deviceIdHashSaltStorage->deleteDeviceIdHashSaltForOrigins(origins, [callbackAggregator] { });
896 }
897
898 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::OfflineWebApplicationCache) && isPersistent()) {
899 HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
900 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
901 for (const auto& origin : dataRecord.origins)
902 origins.add(crossThreadCopy(origin));
903 }
904
905 m_queue->dispatch([origins = WTFMove(origins), applicationCacheDirectory = m_configuration->applicationCacheDirectory().isolatedCopy(), applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName = m_configuration->applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator] {
906 auto storage = WebCore::ApplicationCacheStorage::create(applicationCacheDirectory, applicationCacheFlatFileSubdirectoryName);
907 for (const auto& origin : origins)
908 storage->deleteCacheForOrigin(origin);
909 });
910 }
911
912 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::WebSQLDatabases) && isPersistent()) {
913 HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
914 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
915 for (const auto& origin : dataRecord.origins)
916 origins.add(crossThreadCopy(origin));
917 }
918
919 m_queue->dispatch([origins = WTFMove(origins), callbackAggregator, webSQLDatabaseDirectory = m_configuration->webSQLDatabaseDirectory().isolatedCopy()] {
920 auto databaseTracker = WebCore::DatabaseTracker::trackerWithDatabasePath(webSQLDatabaseDirectory);
921 for (auto& origin : origins)
922 databaseTracker->deleteOrigin(origin);
923 });
924 }
925
926 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::MediaKeys) && isPersistent()) {
927 HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
928 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
929 for (const auto& origin : dataRecord.origins)
930 origins.add(crossThreadCopy(origin));
931 }
932
933 m_queue->dispatch([mediaKeysStorageDirectory = m_configuration->mediaKeysStorageDirectory().isolatedCopy(), callbackAggregator, origins = WTFMove(origins)] {
934 removeMediaKeys(mediaKeysStorageDirectory, origins);
935 });
936 }
937
938#if ENABLE(NETSCAPE_PLUGIN_API)
939 if (dataTypes.contains(WebsiteDataType::PlugInData) && isPersistent()) {
940 Vector<String> hostNames;
941 for (const auto& dataRecord : dataRecords) {
942 for (const auto& hostName : dataRecord.pluginDataHostNames)
943 hostNames.append(hostName);
944 }
945
946
947 class State {
948 public:
949 static void deleteData(Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins, Vector<String>&& hostNames)
950 {
951 new State(WTFMove(callbackAggregator), WTFMove(plugins), WTFMove(hostNames));
952 }
953
954 private:
955 State(Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator>&& callbackAggregator, Vector<PluginModuleInfo>&& plugins, Vector<String>&& hostNames)
956 : m_callbackAggregator(WTFMove(callbackAggregator))
957 , m_plugins(WTFMove(plugins))
958 , m_hostNames(WTFMove(hostNames))
959 {
960 deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
961 }
962
963 ~State()
964 {
965 ASSERT(m_plugins.isEmpty());
966 }
967
968 void deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin()
969 {
970 if (m_plugins.isEmpty()) {
971 delete this;
972 return;
973 }
974
975 auto plugin = m_plugins.takeLast();
976 PluginProcessManager::singleton().deleteWebsiteDataForHostNames(plugin, m_hostNames, [this] {
977 deleteWebsiteDataForNextPlugin();
978 });
979 }
980
981 Ref<RemovalCallbackAggregator> m_callbackAggregator;
982 Vector<PluginModuleInfo> m_plugins;
983 Vector<String> m_hostNames;
984 };
985
986 if (!hostNames.isEmpty())
987 State::deleteData(callbackAggregator.copyRef(), plugins(), WTFMove(hostNames));
988 }
989#endif
990}

1255
1256void WebsiteDataStore::getResourceLoadStatisticsDataSummary(CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1257{
1258 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1259
1260 struct LocalCallbackAggregator : RefCounted<LocalCallbackAggregator> {
1261 LocalCallbackAggregator(CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData>&&)>&& completionHandler)
1262 : m_completionHandler(WTFMove(completionHandler))
1263 {
1264 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1265 };
1266
1267 ~LocalCallbackAggregator()
1268 {
1269 ASSERT(RunLoop::isMain());
1270
1271 m_completionHandler(WTFMove(m_results));
1272 }
1273
1274 void addResult(Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData>&& results)
1275 {
1276 m_results.appendVector(WTFMove(results));
1277 }
1278
1279 CompletionHandler<void(Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData>&&)> m_completionHandler;
1280 Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData> m_results;
1281 };
1282
1283 auto localCallbackAggregator = adoptRef(new LocalCallbackAggregator(WTFMove(completionHandler)));
1284
1285 auto wtfCallbackAggregator = WTF::CallbackAggregator::create([this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this), localCallbackAggregator] {
1286 networkProcess().getResourceLoadStatisticsDataSummary(m_sessionID, [localCallbackAggregator](Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData>&& data) {
1287 localCallbackAggregator->addResult(WTFMove(data));
1288 });
1289 });
1290
1291 for (auto& processPool : WebProcessPool::allProcessPools())
1292 processPool->sendResourceLoadStatisticsDataImmediately([wtfCallbackAggregator] { });
1293}

1618HashSet<RefPtr<WebProcessPool>> WebsiteDataStore::processPools(size_t limit) const
1619{
1620 HashSet<RefPtr<WebProcessPool>> processPools;
1621 for (auto& process : processes()) {
1622 if (auto* processPool = process.processPoolIfExists()) {
1623 processPools.add(processPool);
1624 if (processPools.size() == limit)
1625 break;
1626 }
1627 }
1628
1629 if (processPools.isEmpty()) {
1630 // Check if we're one of the legacy data stores.
1631 for (auto& processPool : WebProcessPool::allProcessPools()) {
1632 processPools.add(processPool.ptr());
1633 if (processPools.size() == limit)
1634 break;
1635 }
1636 }
1637
1638 return processPools;
1639}
1640
1641HashSet<RefPtr<WebProcessPool>> WebsiteDataStore::ensureProcessPools() const
1642{
1643 auto processPools = this->processPools();
1644 if (processPools.isEmpty())
1645 processPools.add(WebProcessPool::create(API::ProcessPoolConfiguration::create()));
1646 return processPools;
1647}

1652 Vector<PluginModuleInfo> plugins;
1653
1654 for (auto& processPool : ensureProcessPools()) {
1655 for (auto& plugin : processPool->pluginInfoStore().plugins())
1656 plugins.append(plugin);

1658
1659 return plugins;
1660}

1663static String computeMediaKeyFile(const String& mediaKeyDirectory)
1664{
1665 return FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(mediaKeyDirectory, "SecureStop.plist");
1666}
1667
1668void WebsiteDataStore::allowSpecificHTTPSCertificateForHost(const WebCertificateInfo* certificate, const String& host)

1672
1673Vector<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> WebsiteDataStore::mediaKeyOrigins(const String& mediaKeysStorageDirectory)
1674{
1675 ASSERT(!mediaKeysStorageDirectory.isEmpty());
1676
1677 Vector<WebCore::SecurityOriginData> origins;
1678
1679 for (const auto& mediaKeyIdentifier : FileSystem::listDirectory(mediaKeysStorageDirectory)) {
1680 auto originPath = FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(mediaKeysStorageDirectory, mediaKeyIdentifier);
1681 auto mediaKeyFile = computeMediaKeyFile(originPath);
1682 if (!FileSystem::fileExists(mediaKeyFile))
1683 continue;
1684
1685 if (auto securityOrigin = WebCore::SecurityOriginData::fromDatabaseIdentifier(mediaKeyIdentifier))
1686 origins.append(*securityOrigin);
1687 }
1688
1689 return origins;
1690}
1691
1692void WebsiteDataStore::removeMediaKeys(const String& mediaKeysStorageDirectory, WallTime modifiedSince)
1693{
1694 ASSERT(!mediaKeysStorageDirectory.isEmpty());
1695
1696 for (const auto& directoryName : FileSystem::listDirectory(mediaKeysStorageDirectory)) {
1697 auto mediaKeyDirectory = FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(mediaKeysStorageDirectory, directoryName);
1698 auto mediaKeyFile = computeMediaKeyFile(mediaKeyDirectory);
1699
1700 auto modificationTime = FileSystem::fileModificationTime(mediaKeyFile);
1701 if (!modificationTime)
1702 continue;
1703
1704 if (modificationTime.value() < modifiedSince)
1705 continue;
1706
1707 FileSystem::deleteFile(mediaKeyFile);
1708 FileSystem::deleteEmptyDirectory(mediaKeyDirectory);
1709 }
1710}
1711
1712void WebsiteDataStore::removeMediaKeys(const String& mediaKeysStorageDirectory, const HashSet<WebCore::SecurityOriginData>& origins)
1713{
1714 ASSERT(!mediaKeysStorageDirectory.isEmpty());
1715
1716 for (const auto& origin : origins) {
1717 auto mediaKeyDirectory = FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(mediaKeysStorageDirectory, origin.databaseIdentifier());
1718 auto mediaKeyFile = computeMediaKeyFile(mediaKeyDirectory);
1719
1720 FileSystem::deleteFile(mediaKeyFile);
1721 FileSystem::deleteEmptyDirectory(mediaKeyDirectory);
1722 }
1723}
1724
1725void WebsiteDataStore::getNetworkProcessConnection(WebProcessProxy& webProcessProxy, CompletionHandler<void(const NetworkProcessConnectionInfo&)>&& reply)
1726{
1727 networkProcess().getNetworkProcessConnection(webProcessProxy, [weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this), webProcessProxy = makeWeakPtr(webProcessProxy), reply = WTFMove(reply)] (auto& connectionInfo) mutable {
1728 if (UNLIKELY(!IPC::Connection::identifierIsValid(connectionInfo.identifier()))) {
1729 // Retry on the next RunLoop iteration because we may be inside the WebsiteDataStore destructor.
1730 RunLoop::main().dispatch([weakThis = WTFMove(weakThis), webProcessProxy = WTFMove(webProcessProxy), reply = WTFMove(reply)] () mutable {
1731 if (RefPtr<WebsiteDataStore> strongThis = weakThis.get(); strongThis && webProcessProxy) {
1732 strongThis->terminateNetworkProcess();
1733 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Process, "getNetworkProcessConnection: Failed first attempt, retrying");
1734 strongThis->networkProcess().getNetworkProcessConnection(*webProcessProxy, WTFMove(reply));
1735 } else
1736 reply({ });
1737 });
1738 return;
1739 }
1740 reply(connectionInfo);
1741 });
1742}

1747 m_networkProcess = nullptr;

1788
1789void WebsiteDataStore::setResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(bool enabled)
1790{
1791#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1792 if (enabled == resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled())
1793 return;
1794
1795 if (enabled) {
1796 m_resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled = true;
1797
1798 resolveDirectoriesIfNecessary();
1799
1800 if (m_networkProcess)
1801 m_networkProcess->send(Messages::NetworkProcess::SetResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(m_sessionID, true), 0);
1802 for (auto& processPool : processPools())
1803 processPool->sendToAllProcessesForSession(Messages::WebProcess::SetResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(true), m_sessionID);
1804 return;
1805 }
1806
1807 if (m_networkProcess)
1808 m_networkProcess->send(Messages::NetworkProcess::SetResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(m_sessionID, false), 0);
1809 for (auto& processPool : processPools())
1810 processPool->sendToAllProcessesForSession(Messages::WebProcess::SetResourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(false), m_sessionID);
1811
1812 m_resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled = false;
1813#else
1814 UNUSED_PARAM(enabled);
1815#endif
1816}

1927WebsiteDataStoreParameters WebsiteDataStore::parameters()
1928{
1929 WebsiteDataStoreParameters parameters;
1930
1931 resolveDirectoriesIfNecessary();
1932
1933 auto resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory = m_configuration->resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory();
1934 SandboxExtension::Handle resourceLoadStatisticsDirectoryHandle;
1935 if (!resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory.isEmpty())
1936 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory, resourceLoadStatisticsDirectoryHandle);
1937
1938 auto networkCacheDirectory = resolvedNetworkCacheDirectory();
1939 SandboxExtension::Handle networkCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle;
1940 if (!networkCacheDirectory.isEmpty())
1941 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(networkCacheDirectory, networkCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle);
1942
1943 auto hstsStorageDirectory = resolvedHSTSStorageDirectory();
1944 SandboxExtension::Handle hstsStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle;
1945 if (!hstsStorageDirectory.isEmpty())
1946 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(hstsStorageDirectory, hstsStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
1947
1948 bool shouldIncludeLocalhostInResourceLoadStatistics = false;
1949 bool enableResourceLoadStatisticsDebugMode = false;
1950 auto firstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode = WebCore::FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::AllButCookies;
1951 WebCore::RegistrableDomain standaloneApplicationDomain;
1952 HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> appBoundDomains;
1953#if ENABLE(APP_BOUND_DOMAINS)
1954 if (isAppBoundITPRelaxationEnabled)
1955 appBoundDomains = appBoundDomainsIfInitialized().value_or(HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain> { });
1956#endif
1957 WebCore::RegistrableDomain resourceLoadStatisticsManualPrevalentResource;
1958 ResourceLoadStatisticsParameters resourceLoadStatisticsParameters = {
1959 WTFMove(resourceLoadStatisticsDirectory),
1960 WTFMove(resourceLoadStatisticsDirectoryHandle),
1961 resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled(),
1962#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1963 isItpStateExplicitlySet(),
1964 hasStatisticsTestingCallback(),
1965#else
1966 false,
1967 false,
1968#endif
1969 shouldIncludeLocalhostInResourceLoadStatistics,
1970 enableResourceLoadStatisticsDebugMode,
1971#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
1972 thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode(),
1973 WebCore::SameSiteStrictEnforcementEnabled::No,
1974#endif
1975 firstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode,
1976 WTFMove(standaloneApplicationDomain),
1977 WTFMove(appBoundDomains),
1978 WTFMove(resourceLoadStatisticsManualPrevalentResource),
1979 };
1980
1981 NetworkSessionCreationParameters networkSessionParameters;
1982 networkSessionParameters.sessionID = m_sessionID;
1983 networkSessionParameters.boundInterfaceIdentifier = configuration().boundInterfaceIdentifier();
1984 networkSessionParameters.allowsCellularAccess = configuration().allowsCellularAccess() ? AllowsCellularAccess::Yes : AllowsCellularAccess::No;
1985 networkSessionParameters.deviceManagementRestrictionsEnabled = m_configuration->deviceManagementRestrictionsEnabled();
1986 networkSessionParameters.allLoadsBlockedByDeviceManagementRestrictionsForTesting = m_configuration->allLoadsBlockedByDeviceManagementRestrictionsForTesting();
1987 networkSessionParameters.networkCacheDirectory = WTFMove(networkCacheDirectory);
1988 networkSessionParameters.networkCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle = WTFMove(networkCacheDirectoryExtensionHandle);
1989 networkSessionParameters.hstsStorageDirectory = WTFMove(hstsStorageDirectory);
1990 networkSessionParameters.hstsStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle = WTFMove(hstsStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
1991 networkSessionParameters.dataConnectionServiceType = m_configuration->dataConnectionServiceType();
1992 networkSessionParameters.fastServerTrustEvaluationEnabled = m_configuration->fastServerTrustEvaluationEnabled();
1993 networkSessionParameters.networkCacheSpeculativeValidationEnabled = m_configuration->networkCacheSpeculativeValidationEnabled();
1994 networkSessionParameters.shouldUseTestingNetworkSession = m_configuration->testingSessionEnabled();
1995 networkSessionParameters.staleWhileRevalidateEnabled = m_configuration->staleWhileRevalidateEnabled();
1996 networkSessionParameters.testSpeedMultiplier = m_configuration->testSpeedMultiplier();
1997 networkSessionParameters.suppressesConnectionTerminationOnSystemChange = m_configuration->suppressesConnectionTerminationOnSystemChange();
1998 networkSessionParameters.allowsServerPreconnect = m_configuration->allowsServerPreconnect();
1999 networkSessionParameters.resourceLoadStatisticsParameters = WTFMove(resourceLoadStatisticsParameters);
2000 networkSessionParameters.requiresSecureHTTPSProxyConnection = m_configuration->requiresSecureHTTPSProxyConnection();
2001 networkSessionParameters.preventsSystemHTTPProxyAuthentication = m_configuration->preventsSystemHTTPProxyAuthentication();
2002
2003 parameters.networkSessionParameters = WTFMove(networkSessionParameters);
2004
2005 parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectory = resolvedIndexedDatabaseDirectory();
2006 if (!parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectory.isEmpty())
2007 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectory, parameters.indexedDatabaseDirectoryExtensionHandle);
2008
2009#if ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
2010 parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory = resolvedServiceWorkerRegistrationDirectory();
2011 if (!parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory.isEmpty())
2012 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectory, parameters.serviceWorkerRegistrationDirectoryExtensionHandle);
2013 parameters.serviceWorkerProcessTerminationDelayEnabled = m_configuration->serviceWorkerProcessTerminationDelayEnabled();
2014#endif
2015
2016 auto localStorageDirectory = resolvedLocalStorageDirectory();
2017 if (!localStorageDirectory.isEmpty()) {
2018 parameters.localStorageDirectory = localStorageDirectory;
2019 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(localStorageDirectory, parameters.localStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
2020 }
2021
2022 auto cacheStorageDirectory = this->cacheStorageDirectory();
2023 if (!cacheStorageDirectory.isEmpty()) {
2024 parameters.cacheStorageDirectory = cacheStorageDirectory;
2025 SandboxExtension::createHandleForReadWriteDirectory(cacheStorageDirectory, parameters.cacheStorageDirectoryExtensionHandle);
2026 }
2027
2028 parameters.perOriginStorageQuota = perOriginStorageQuota();
2029 parameters.perThirdPartyOriginStorageQuota = perThirdPartyOriginStorageQuota();
2030
2031#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
2032 parameters.networkSessionParameters.resourceLoadStatisticsParameters.enabled = m_resourceLoadStatisticsEnabled;
2033#endif
2034 platformSetNetworkParameters(parameters);
2035#if PLATFORM(COCOA)
2036 parameters.networkSessionParameters.appHasRequestedCrossWebsiteTrackingPermission = hasRequestedCrossWebsiteTrackingPermission();
2037 parameters.networkSessionParameters.useNetworkLoader = useNetworkLoader();
2038#endif
2039
2040 return parameters;
2041}

2141void WebsiteDataStore::forwardAppBoundDomainsToITPIfInitialized(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
2142{
2143 auto callbackAggregator = CallbackAggregator::create(WTFMove(completionHandler));
2144 auto appBoundDomains = appBoundDomainsIfInitialized();
2145 if (!appBoundDomains)
2146 return;
2147
2148 auto propagateAppBoundDomains = [callbackAggregator] (WebsiteDataStore* store, const HashSet<WebCore::RegistrableDomain>& domains) {
2149 if (!store)
2150 return;
2151
2152 if (store->thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode() != WebCore::ThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode::AllExceptBetweenAppBoundDomains)
2153 store->setThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode(WebCore::ThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode::AllExceptBetweenAppBoundDomains, [callbackAggregator] { });
2154
2155 store->setAppBoundDomainsForITP(domains, [callbackAggregator] { });
2156 };
2157
2158 propagateAppBoundDomains(globalDefaultDataStore().get(), *appBoundDomains);
2159
2160 for (auto* store : allDataStores().values())
2161 propagateAppBoundDomains(store, *appBoundDomains);
2162}
